---
alwaysApply: false
---
Service Layer
Format: {Verb} + {Target}
Class Name: {Noun}Service
Commonly Used Verbs:
fetch: Retrieve a single record
fetchList: Retrieve multiple records
create: Create a new record
update: Update a single record
bulkUpdate: Update multiple records
destroy: Delete a single record
bulkDestroy: Delete multiple records
count: Count the number of records
exists: Check for existence

Repository Layer
Format: {Verb} + {Target}
Class Name: {Noun}Repository
Commonly Used Verbs:
find: Retrieve a single record
search: Search for multiple records
insert: Add a single record
bulkInsert: Add multiple records
update: Update a single record
bulkUpdate: Update multiple records
delete: Delete a single record
bulkDelete: Delete multiple records

Controller Layer
Format: {Verb} + {Target}
Class Name: {Noun}Controller (assumed, as not specified)
Commonly Used Verbs:
index: Display a list
create: Display a form for creating a new record
store: Process the creation of a new record
show: Display details of a single record
edit: Display a form for editing a record
update: Process the update of a record
destroy: Process the deletion of a single record
bulkDestroy: Process the deletion of multiple records
